Every file that needs to be added to the store HAS TO BE added in git!
```
sudo ln -s ~/nixos-config/ /etc/nixos
```

# My personalized work setup
Currently using Hyprland with mostly rose-pine colors, wezterm and neovim through nixvim with my own [config](https://github.com/BenjaminTalbi/my-nixvim)

